## 二、Risk Factors 风险信号提取

### 信号1：资产减值风险（Risk Factors 第2478-2480行）

> **原文**：
> "charges associated with impairment or abandonment of any assets on our balance sheet, including as a result of changes to our real property lease arrangements and data center assets"

> **提取**：
> - 公司承认数据中心资产可能减值或废弃
> - 原因：房地产租赁变更、数据中心资产变化
> - **信号强度**：中等（直接提及减值，但原因偏外部）

### 信号2：技术基础设施减值风险（Risk Factors 第2681-2683行）

> **原文**：
> "or impairment of assets on our balance sheet. For example, like others in our industry, we rely on certain third-party equipment and components for our technical infrastructure that are manufactured by a small number of third parties"

> **提取**：
> - 公司承认技术基础设施资产可能减值
> - 原因：依赖少数第三方供应商的设备
> - 供应链风险导致资产减值
> - **信号强度**：中等（供应链风险→资产减值）

### 信号3：外国政府导致的技术基础设施减值（Risk Factors 第2700-2702行）

> **原文**：
> "has resulted, and may result in the future, in the impairment of a portion of our technical infrastructure, which may interrupt the delivery or degrade the quality or reliability of our products"

> **提取**：
> - 外国政府行动已导致部分技术基础设施减值
> - 未来可能继续发生
> - **信号强度**：较高（已发生+可能继续）

### 信号4：收购相关无形资产风险（Risk Factors 第3085-3087行）

> **原文**：
> "Acquisitions or other strategic transactions may also result in our recording of significant additional expenses to our results of operations and recording of substantial finite-lived intangible assets on our balance sheet upon closing"

> **提取**：
> - 收购导致大量无形资产入账
> - 这些无形资产可能减值
> - 商誉$20,654M，一旦减值影响巨大
> - **信号强度**：中等（风险存在但非直接折旧问题）

### 信号5：商誉和无形资产减值（Risk Factors 第3261-3271行）

> **原文**：
> "If our goodwill or intangible assets become impaired, we may be required to record a significant charge to earnings. We review our intangible assets for impairment when events or changes in circumstances indicate the carrying value may not be recoverable, such as a decline in stock price and market capitalization. We test goodwill for impairment at the reporting unit level at least annually."

> **提取**：
> - 公司明确承认商誉和无形资产可能减值
> - 触发条件：股价下跌、市值缩水
> - 每年至少测试一次商誉减值
> - 商誉$20,654M，占无形资产绝大部分
> - **信号强度**：较高（$20B+商誉，一旦减值影响巨大）

### 信号6：会计政策 - 折旧方法（Note 1, 第6214-6218行）

> **原文**：
> "Property and equipment, including finance leases, are depreciated and stated at cost less accumulated depreciation. Depreciation is computed using the straight-line method over the estimated useful lives of the assets or the remaining lease term, whichever is shorter."

> **提取**：
> - 折旧方法：直线法
> - 按预计使用寿命或剩余租期（取短者）
> - 服务器和网络资产：4-5年
> - 建筑物：25-30年
> - 设备和其他：1-3年
> - **信号强度**：关键数据（直接决定折旧政策）

### 信号7：资产估值判断（Note 1, 第5312-5316行）

> **原文**：
> "The valuation and impairment assessment of certain assets, including recoverability, requires significant judgment and assumptions such as estimation of future cash flows, discount rates, market data of comparable assets and companies, holding period and residual value of asset groups, among others."

> **提取**：
> - 资产估值需要"重大判断和假设"
> - 涉及未来现金流估计、折现率、可比资产数据等
> - 主观性强，存在管理层操纵空间
> - **信号强度**：中等（主观判断→估计偏差风险）

### 信号8：运营费用中的折旧构成（Note 1, 第6044-6046行）

> **原文**：
> "depreciation expense from servers, network infrastructure and buildings, as well as payroll and related expenses which include share-based compensation for employees on our operations teams, and energy and bandwidth costs"

> **提取**：
> - 服务器、网络基础设施和建筑物的折旧费用
> - 是运营费用的重要组成部分
> - 服务器折旧$7,320M（占折旧总额65%）
> - **信号强度**：关键数据（说明服务器折旧是核心成本）

